Who Do You Think You Are? Australia - Series 7, Episode 6




Peter Rowsthorn

Actor and comedian Peter Rowsthorn turns his attention towards his early Australian family, and much to his delight, discovers he has two convicts in his family tree. Then, a long held family secret is revealed with Peter discovering a grandfather he never knew. The new connection to his grandfather sees Peter pondering whether to change his surname to better reflect his real heritage.




Original Air Date: 08-Sep-2015
